          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover " href="/book/show/40727012-manuscript-for-murder">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2564021182" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4904920118445629038">This story was s little different from the usual Murder she wrote books. Having a second author changes things with quick reads since not used to this other author. I did enjoy the very different kind of mystery and will probably read it again when others are not waiting.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


